2:T712,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Lumen5 better than Steve AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Lumen5 scores 6.0 overall while Steve AI scores 6.0. Lumen5 is best for content marketers and repurposing blog content to video, while Steve AI excels for animated explainer videos and educational content."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Lumen5 or Steve AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Lumen5 starts at $19/mo and Steve AI starts at $20/mo. Lumen5 offers a free plan. Steve AI offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Lumen5 to Steve AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Lumen5 and Steve AI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Lumen5 vs Steve AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Lumen5 holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10. Steve AI has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Lumen5 for blog-to-video automation and Steve AI for good animation styles."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Lumen5 or Steve AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Lumen5 for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Steve AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize good animation styles. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"c