8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Lumen5 and Steve AI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Video, Auto Captions, Templates, Stock Footage. Interestingly, both platforms offer nearly identical feature sets. The difference lies more in the implementation quality and depth of each feature rather than feature availability itself. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Lumen5 holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Steve AI scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Lumen5 offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $19/mo, compared to Steve AI's starting price of $20/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Lumen5's free tier and Steve AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
