c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Lumen5 is best suited for content marketers, repurposing blog content to video, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Steve AI, meanwhile, shines for animated explainer videos, educational content, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2017, Lumen5 describes itself as \"Turn blog posts and articles into engaging videos.\" Steve AI, established in 2021, positions itself as \"Create animated and live-action videos with AI.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Lumen5** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Steve AI is a poor choice — far from it. Steve AI excels in its own right, particularly for animated explainer videos and educational content.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value blog-to-video automation, go with Lumen5. If good animation styles matters more to you, Steve AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
